  lighttpd-1.4.25-r1.ebuild:
  stable x86, security bug 303213

  02 Feb 2010; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> lighttpd-1.4.25-r1.ebuild:
  Marking lighttpd-1.4.25-r1 ppc64 for bug 303213

